  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exocraft Hazard Protection Unit",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "强化艇危险防护单元",
    "TraditionalChinese": "強化艇風險防護裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Sublimation cooling vents and high-thermal mass buffers are installed in all structural panels, keeping the Exocraft pilot at non-lethal temperatures even in the most overwhelming of firestorms.<br><br>Entirely prevents all damage or energy drain while inside an Exocraft in <span class=\"name name-fuel\">scorched environments</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在所有的结构面板上安装升华冷却通风口和高热质量缓冲层，确保强化艇即使是进入最猛烈的火焰风暴中，也能保证飞船驾驶员在非致命的温度下驾驶。<br><br>在强化艇中时可完全避免<span class=\"name name-fuel\">炙热环境</span>下的所有伤害或能量消耗。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在所有結構面板加裝昇華冷卻通風管以及高熱質量緩衝器，即便在最嚴峻的火焰風暴中，強化艇駕駛員也不會身處致命的溫度。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">灼熱環境</span>下待在強化艇中，能避免任何損害或能量消耗。"
  },
